    <title>远程控制+Sakurafrp实现非局域网远程控制</title>
    <url>/2021/11/08/python/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、下载RD-Client"><a href="#一、下载RD-Client" class="headerlink" title="一、下载RD Client"></a>一、下载RD Client</h2><ul>
<li>安卓端网页下载或者<a href="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/base.apk">RDClient</a></li>
<li>ios端在App Store搜索RDClient</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二、设置PC允许远程连接"><a href="#二、设置PC允许远程连接" class="headerlink" title="二、设置PC允许远程连接"></a>二、设置PC允许远程连接</h2><ul>
<li><strong>win11</strong>：这里打开电脑设置-&gt; 系统-&gt;远程桌面</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720211109094906.png" alt="QQ图片20211109094906"></p>
<p>==这里的打开后你能连接你的用户就是你电脑开机时的用户，例如administrator，win10也是一样的==</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>win10</strong>：</li>
</ul>
<p> 进入控制面板-&gt;系统和安全-&gt;系统-&gt;远程设置<br>按照下图方式勾选<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdn.net/20170215163223342?watermark/2/text/aHR0cDovL2Jsb2cuY3Nkbi5uZXQvcXFfMzA0NjU2NTc=/font/5a6L5L2T/fontsize/400/fill/I0JBQkFCMA==/dissolve/70/gravity/SouthEast" alt="这里写图片描述"></p>
<h2 id="三、注册sakura-frp（需要实名认证，支付宝授权就行）"><a href="#三、注册sakura-frp（需要实名认证，支付宝授权就行）" class="headerlink" title="三、注册sakura frp（需要实名认证，支付宝授权就行）"></a>三、注册sakura frp（需要实名认证，支付宝授权就行）</h2><p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109101421526.png" alt="image-20211109101421526"></p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109101508848.png" alt="image-20211109101508848"></p>
<p>在导航栏上</p>
<p>用户-&gt;实名认证</p>
<p>根据提示完成认证</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109101620430.png" alt="image-20211109101620430"></p>
<p>点击穿透-&gt;隧道列表</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109101742287.png" alt="image-20211109101742287"></p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109102002178.png" alt="image-20211109102002178"></p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109102044910.png" alt="image-20211109102044910"></p>
<p>点击软件下载</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109102209378.png" alt="image-20211109102209378"></p>
<p>然后解压安装</p>
<p>再打开frpc.ini配置文件（可以用记事本打开）</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103125704.png" alt="image-20211109103125704"></p>
<p>再去sakura frp网站点击<strong>隧道列表</strong>，找到你刚才新建的隧道</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103347791.png" alt="image-20211109103347791"></p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103506496.png" alt="image-20211109103506496"></p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103555304.png" alt="image-20211109103555304"></p>
<p>然后直接去刚才打开的frpc.ini粘贴即可。</p>
<p>最后直接打开exe</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103722486.png" alt="image-20211109103722486"></p>
<p>运行结果：然后缩小，去平板或者手机或者pc连接电脑</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109103802090.png" alt="image-20211109103802090"></p>
<h2 id="四、连接电脑"><a href="#四、连接电脑" class="headerlink" title="四、连接电脑"></a>四、连接电脑</h2><p>点击Desktop</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109104240443.png" alt="image-20211109104240443"></p>
<p>然后add MANUALLY</p>
<p><img src="https://presenter.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image-20211109104948381.png" alt="image-20211109104948381"></p>
<p>然后点击save就行</p>
<p>最后直接连接</p>
]]></content>
